data.description: Under Construction. The CORDALE is great for entertaining with the cafe just off the kitchen for casual dining. The master bedroom conveniently located on the first floor with a bathroom that features double sink with granite tops. Our amenities feature 2 beautiful clubhouses with 2 resort style pools,2 fitness centers, putt-putt golf, beach volleyball, tennis , lake view BBQ/picnic area, dog-park and so much more. Come out and see all of our beautiful decorated models and view the community that is a "must see" in Winter Garden/Horizons West. *Photos are of similar model but not that of exact house. Pictures, photographs, colors, features, and sizes are for illustration purposes only and will vary from the homes as built. Home and community information including pricing, included features, terms, availability and amenities are subject to change and prior sale at any time without notice or obligation. Please note that no representations or warranties are made regarding school districts or school assignments; you should conduct your own investigation regarding current and future schools and school boundaries.*
